I'm slowly whittling away at my set and still have these holes to fill. Ideal cards have clean fronts (VG-VG/EX eye appeal with nice registration) though technical grade isn't so important. I do ask that they have no creases or pinholes, though. Staining, paper loss, etc. are ok on the backs. Raw is fine. Thanks for looking.
